Dialogue: 10,0:00:02.96,0:00:04.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ledakan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.96,0:00:07.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak bisa bergerak di udara!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.07,0:00:10.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku meledakkan lantai setinggi tiga tingkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.40,0:00:12.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jatuh bebas ini mengunci akselerasinya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.80,0:00:14.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Shotgun!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:14.45,0:00:16.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau butuh kaki untuk mendarat.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:26.82,0:00:29.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang sekali, Guru.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.36,0:00:34.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seharusnya kau langsung tembus kepalaku\Ntanpa ragu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:53.63,0:00:55.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Guru!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:55.41,0:01:00.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau memang yang terbaik!\NKeren sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.50,0:01:02.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih dari para pro yang tak jelas itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.86,0:01:05.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bahkan lebih dari All Might!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:05.03,0:01:07.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jauh lebih keren!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:08.23,0:01:11.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku akan melampauimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.03,0:01:13.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,O'Clock yang melampaui O'Clock.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.63,0:01:16.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan jadi satu-satunya di dunia ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:17.23,0:01:19.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Khayalan yang sangat konyol.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:19.40,0:01:22.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berdiri setelah ledakan itu saja\Nkau sudah kepayahan.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:23.36,0:01:26.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kuhajar sampai kau\Ntak bisa bangun lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:27.46,0:01:31.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau akan tumbang di sini\Ndan tak jadi siapa-siapa.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:31.74,0:01:35.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pikir aku cuma peniru, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:35.80,0:01:38.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang, kau jauh lebih paham
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.70,0:01:42.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,tentang Quirk O'Clock, Overclock.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:42.36,0:01:44.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja, lebih dariku.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:44.95,0:01:48.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi kau belum tahu tentangku.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:49.16,0:01:51.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Misalnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.40,0:01:56.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga bisa melakukan ini\Ndengan Overclock.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.86,0:02:00.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mempercepat pertumbuhan sel, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.85,0:02:05.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lengan kananku juga bom!\NDaya hancurnya maksimal!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.76,0:02:09.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi kau bilang tempat ini kandang?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau peti?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.02,0:02:17.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Intinya, kalau aku ledakkan\Ndinding ini besertamu, aku bisa kabur, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.15,0:02:17.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.58,0:02:21.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kubuat kau pingsan sebelum itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.08,0:02:25.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu dia!\NMelangkah maju tanpa ragu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tekad itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.23,0:02:32.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang... keren sekali!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.14,0:02:45.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Barusan,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.83,0:02:48.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku dengar suara ledakan dari kejauhan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.63,0:04:34.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Chris!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.05,0:04:35.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepat sembuh, ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.55,0:04:37.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunjukkanlah wajahmu, meski cuma sebentar!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.66,0:04:41.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di luar ramai sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.00,0:04:44.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Telepon media di kantor\Njuga tak berhenti berdering.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.32,0:04:46.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka terus meminta komentar singkat.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.55,0:04:48.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku lihat di TV.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.56,0:04:50.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Best Jeanist dan yang lain...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.39,0:04:55.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kata mereka, C.C. berjasa setelah All Might.\NDia pahlawan di balik layar, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.66,0:04:58.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berkat itu, efek promosinya luar biasa.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.77,0:05:00.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, Koichi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.80,0:05:04.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku malah mengambil semua pujian,\Ntermasuk milikmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.30,0:05:07.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, tidak apa-apa soal itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.16,0:05:10.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari itu aku nyaris mati beberapa kali,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.00,0:05:13.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi dapat tanda tangan All Might\Ndi hoodie-ku.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.12,0:05:17.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, jatuhnya malah untung.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.06,0:05:18.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Murah banget nyawamu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.90,0:05:20.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bodoh, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.10,0:05:22.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harusnya kau lebih waspada bahaya!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:23.55,0:05:28.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,orang sepertiku yang melawan\Npenjahat sembarangan, takkan dipuji.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.39,0:05:31.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Malah akan ditangkap kalau ketahuan, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.70,0:05:33.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:33.22,0:05:37.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Polisi juga sudah memperingatkan soal itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.25,0:05:38.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, polisi?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.58,0:05:40.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ketahuan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.03,0:05:41.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.09,0:05:45.23,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Makoto, soal penanganan anak itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:45.24,0:05:47.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak itu maksudnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.11,0:05:51.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Vigilante Naruhata\Nyang menyebut dirinya The Crawler.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.37,0:05:54.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah dengar banyak dari Eraser.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.39,0:05:54.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.90,0:05:59.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam insiden ini, dia bekerja sama\Ndengan Captain Celebrity
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.19,0:06:01.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan menyelamatkan banyak nyawa.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.66,0:06:05.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebenarnya dia pantas diberi\Npenghargaan resmi, tetapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.63,0:06:10.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aksi vigilante yang selama ini\Ndia lakukan juga akan ikut disorot.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.45,0:06:15.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, kita tak bisa\Nmenghindari pemberian sanksi.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.63,0:06:18.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena itu, kali ini kita anggap jasa\Ndan kesalahannya impas.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.73,0:06:24.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami sudah meminta pihak terkait\Nuntuk tidak menyinggung anak berhoodie itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:24.57,0:06:29.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengerti? Ini murni\Nditoleransi karena jasanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.30,0:06:34.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan sampai dia dipuja-puja sebagai\NPahlawan Sky Egg atau semacamnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.76,0:06:36.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh, begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, ada cara seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.76,0:06:41.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuma bercanda!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.86,0:06:44.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hal seperti penghargaan atau pujaan...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.56,0:06:48.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sebenarnya tak menginginkan semua itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu salah satu kelebihannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sipil yang berniat baik, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.43,0:06:56.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu orang seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.23,0:06:59.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Secara pribadi, aku juga...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.23,0:07:03.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh ya, kakakku juga\Nmengucapkan terima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.90,0:07:05.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kakakmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.57,0:07:08.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia terlibat dalam kejadian itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.15,0:07:12.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mungkin dia berterima kasih\Nsebagai kakakku?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian berdua dekat, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.43,0:07:16.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, kurang lebih begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.09,0:07:19.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei! Tolong beri jalan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.51,0:07:21.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku buru-buru! Minggir!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Chris!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.35,0:07:23.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.06,0:07:26.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.13,0:07:29.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:29.22,0:07:31.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar bodoh! Apa yang kau lakukan?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak! Sayang, tunggu!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.89,0:07:36.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Patah tulangku sudah cukup banyak!\NSerius, sudah banyak!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:36.89,0:07:39.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, tolong pelan-pelan!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.02,0:07:40.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sedang terluka!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.40,0:07:48.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau aksimu itu membuatmu mati?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.03,0:07:48.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar bodoh.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.24,0:07:53.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, Sayang.\NAku cuma ingin terlihat keren.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.20,0:07:55.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Untukmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.62,0:08:02.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau Koichi, ya?\NAku sudah dengar dari Makoto.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.08,0:08:06.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih sudah menyelamatkan kekasihku.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.54,0:08:07.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sama-sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.93,0:08:12.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah, sesekali dapat ucapan terima kasih\Nternyata enak juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.76,0:08:15.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selama ini aku juga\Nberterima kasih padamu, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.90,0:08:19.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tadi kau juga sudah dapat\Nterima kasih dari kakakku, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.70,0:08:20.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.90,0:08:24.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia memang tak pernah benar-benar menyimak.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.38,0:08:34.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Panggilan terakhir untuk penerbangan\NANF-6N tujuan New York.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.19,0:08:35.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Agak memalukan pakai kostum begini\Ndi bandara.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.99,0:08:38.79,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Penumpang dimohon segera menuju Gerbang 55.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.83,0:08:38.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, namanya juga perayaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.60,0:08:40.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makoto belum datang?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:40.80,0:08:42.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya akan mepet.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.26,0:08:45.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, itu Captain!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.90,0:08:47.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua, siap-siap!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:48.83,0:08:50.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satu, dua!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,CAPTAIN!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.59,0:08:54.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.47,0:08:56.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Captain Celebrity!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.63,0:08:59.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat atas kepulangan\Ndan kesembuhan Anda!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.36,0:09:02.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa beri komentar singkat\Nsoal aktivitas Anda di Jepang?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.00,0:09:08.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, memang sebentar,\Ntapi aku senang berkunjung kemari.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.03,0:09:13.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini seperti titik balik dalam hidupku,\Nseperti terlahir kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.41,0:09:15.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Naruhata seperti kampung halaman keduaku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.19,0:09:19.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku takkan melupakan semua orang\Nyang kutemui di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.12,0:09:21.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Captain...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.10,0:09:23.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja aku berterima kasih\Nkepada semua orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.54,0:09:27.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi ada dua orang\Nyang sangat berjasa bagiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.21,0:09:29.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dua orang?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.10,0:09:32.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama adalah Makoto, manajerku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.88,0:09:36.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sungguh, dia adalah dewi bagiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.80,0:09:39.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pengakuan mengejutkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.30,0:09:43.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apakah dia wanita yang dekat\Ndengan Anda di Jepang?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.06,0:09:46.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Tunggu, bukan begitu maksudnya...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.77,0:09:49.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sayang, tolong jelaskan pada mereka!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.70,0:09:51.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Urus saja sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.96,0:09:57.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf aku terlambat! Jalanan macet!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.34,0:09:59.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, itu Makoto!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.63,0:10:01.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Katanya Makoto?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.53,0:10:04.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anda manajer yang dibicarakan itu?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.30,0:10:06.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa hubungan Anda dengan Captain Celebrity?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.25,0:10:07.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apakah istrinya tahu soal ini?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.96,0:10:13.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kujawab pertanyaan kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.10,0:10:14.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memang benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.04,0:10:19.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yang paling sering\Nbersama Captain Celebrity di Jepang.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:19.70,0:10:22.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, ini bukan hubungan asmara.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.66,0:10:26.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia mendedikasikan seluruh waktunya\Nuntuk pekerjaan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:26.73,0:10:31.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu, Captain, siapa satu penolong lagi\Nyang Anda sebutkan tadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.46,0:10:33.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.00,0:10:36.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, maaf. Saat ini belum bisa kukatakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:36.66,0:10:39.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu berarti hubungan\Nyang tak bisa dipublikasikan?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.74,0:10:42.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh, tunggu dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.10,0:10:47.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia adalah sosok pahlawan pribadi\Nyang sangat dihormati Captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.36,0:10:52.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun, karena skandal masa lalu C.C.,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.11,0:10:56.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,kami sangat berhati-hati mengungkap\Nidentitas orang tersebut.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:57.21,0:10:58.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah maksudku!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hebat ya, Makoto.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.56,0:11:01.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sangat bisa diandalkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.96,0:11:05.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pahlawan yang dia hormati...\NMungkin All Might, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.06,0:11:08.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makoto, terima kasih atas segalanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.50,0:11:12.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jujur, aku tak yakin karierku di Amerika\Nakan lancar nanti,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku akan berusaha.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.15,0:11:16.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akan kulakukan semampuku terlebih dahulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.86,0:11:19.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika belum cukup, aku akan mengandalkan\Norang-orang di sekitarku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.43,0:11:22.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, silakan terus mengandalkanku\Nke depannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.80,0:11:23.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.76,0:11:24.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:24.60,0:11:28.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai musim semi ini, aku akan kuliah\Ndi universitas di New York.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.56,0:11:32.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan tetap bekerja sebagai\Nmanajer C.C., tenang saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.25,0:11:34.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?! Aku tak pernah dengar soal itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.96,0:11:36.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semuanya sudah diatur, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.92,0:11:39.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harusnya kau bilang dari awal, Sayang!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.40,0:11:48.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat tinggal!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.02,0:11:56.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jaga diri kalian! Nanti kuhubungi lagi!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.36,0:12:01.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa, Makoto!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Wah. Makoto kuliah di luar negeri, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.90,0:12:16.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keren banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.96,0:12:21.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, dia memang bukan tipe orang yang\Nakan berdiam diri di Jepang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.05,0:12:23.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nih, kopi.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.76,0:12:28.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Caranya menjawab wawancara sangat lancar.\NKeren sekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.20,0:12:31.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koichi juga seharusnya bisa lebih diakui.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.26,0:12:35.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hah? Kenapa? Kau kan selalu bilang\Naku harus tahu diri.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iya sih, tapi...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.43,0:12:40.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mempertaruhkan nyawa\Nuntuk menolong orang,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:40.53,0:12:43.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi rasanya kau kurang dihargai.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.36,0:12:48.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, memang. Bohong kalau kubilang\Naku tak ingin diakui orang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Nsesekali kau saja yang memujiku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.77,0:12:55.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak bisa memintanya begitu saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.86,0:13:01.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Inilah akhir dari insiden Sky Egg\Ndi tahun pertamaku sebagai Crawler.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.13,0:13:05.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagi publik, itu adalah insiden besar,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.36,0:13:08.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi aku hanya kebetulan ada di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:08.43,0:13:12.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebaliknya, ada yang memilih terus terjun\Nke situasi hidup dan mati seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:12.16,0:13:15.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itulah yang membuat Pahlawan Pro\Nterlihat menakjubkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.52,0:13:18.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitulah pikirku saat itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.26,0:13:23.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pak Tanuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.50,0:13:26.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hasil forensik sudah keluar.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.80,0:13:32.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dari dua sampel darah di lokasi kejadian,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.71,0:13:35.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,satu teridentifikasi sebagai milik\NPahlawan Super Cepat O'Clock.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:35.30,0:13:39.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nama aslinya Oguro Iwao, 45 tahun,\Nmantan pahlawan pro.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.71,0:13:43.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seperti dugaanku, yang itu sudah jelas.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.20,0:13:44.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang satu lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.03,0:13:48.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mengandung berbagai zat kimia\Nberkonsentrasi tinggi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:48.00,0:13:51.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Golongan darah dan DNA-nya\Ntak bisa diidentifikasi.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:51.93,0:13:54.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Statusnya tak diketahui.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.60,0:13:58.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,O'Clock...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:58.23,0:14:02.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau bertarung dengan apa di sini?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.36,0:14:06.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang sedang kami kejar itu...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:06.86,0:14:09.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apakah benar-benar manusia?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:19.40,0:14:21.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di Kota Naruhata...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.56,0:14:22.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kyaa!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.76,0:14:27.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini pun banyak orang yang kelihatannya\Nseperti penjahat berandalan!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei, hei, Nona-nona.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.40,0:14:33.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menabrak orang lalu cuma teriak\N"kyaa" itu tak sopan, tahu?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.31,0:14:37.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih tepatnya mereka memang tinggal\Ndi sekitar sini, jadi selalu ada!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:37.89,0:14:41.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bos, sepertinya tanganku patah.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.70,0:14:47.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hati dan tubuh kami yang sensitif\Nini terluka, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:47.96,0:14:51.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami cuma minta iktikad baik, kok.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.00,0:14:52.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Iktikad baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.32,0:14:54.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ngapain kalian lihat-lihat, hah?!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:55.83,0:15:01.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tahu, tidak? Di sini polisi dan pahlawan\Njarang datang.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:01.43,0:15:06.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Masuk sedikit ke gang belakang,\Ntakkan ada yang menolong kalian.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.10,0:15:07.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo jalan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:07.03,0:15:08.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga tahu!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.38,0:15:13.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sekitar Stasiun Naruhata ada pahlawan\Nyang selalu datang bila dipanggil!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:15.80,0:15:19.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Legenda penyelamat samar macam apa itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:19.76,0:15:21.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cerita begitu tidak bisa diandalkan...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.56,0:15:23.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,THE CRAWLER!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.36,0:15:25.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namun...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.95,0:15:29.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar! Di Naruhata, dia juga ada!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:29.53,0:15:31.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hai, hai!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.10,0:15:34.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia juga tinggal di sekitar sini,\Ndan hampir selalu ada!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku paling senang kalau namaku\Ndisebut dengan benar!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:38.16,0:15:40.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,The Crawler!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.04,0:15:41.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Sialan! Kau!\N- Akhirnya muncul!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:41.37,0:15:44.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, bertahun-tahun aku dipanggil\Nsi Howler, si Howler...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.80,0:15:46.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar kecoak!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pria berhoodie norak menjijikkan!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:47.46,0:15:49.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitulah panggilanku selama ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi akhir-akhir ini aku berpikir.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.97,0:15:59.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika aku terus berusaha dengan tekun,\Npasti ada juga yang akan mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:59.93,0:16:02.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perhatikan sekitarmu saat bertarung!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan menghindar terus!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:05.26,0:16:07.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semangat, Crawler!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.06,0:16:08.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo Howler, taklukkan mereka!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.86,0:16:10.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan terbawa suasana!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.30,0:16:11.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sialan kau...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:11.92,0:16:13.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan main-main denganku!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:17.58,0:16:19.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gaya serangan tusuk!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.83,0:16:21.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gaya serangan tusuk!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.76,0:16:25.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan sekarang... KGD dengan kedua tangan!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.30,0:16:28.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku berhasil.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.81,0:16:30.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar kau.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:30.68,0:16:31.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bercanda!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.56,0:16:36.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hei!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:36.35,0:16:37.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh, sakit!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.64,0:16:39.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi kalian, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.43,0:16:42.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berandalan yang bikin keributan di kota.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.66,0:16:44.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Apa sih, kalian ini?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.76,0:16:48.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami ini kedai dengan pria bertubuh besar\Nelegan dan seekor kucing lucu!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:49.03,0:16:50.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di Naruhata Timur...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:50.53,0:16:52.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hopper's Cafe!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:53.36,0:16:54.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku stafnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.97,0:16:56.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Aku cuma pekerja paruh waktu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku pemiliknya, lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.96,0:17:00.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang-orang seperti kalian ini...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:00.86,0:17:06.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Norak, miskin, dan hidupnya tak beres.\NMakanya jadi sampah masyarakat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.16,0:17:11.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tak mau diseret polisi, mending\Nbekerja dan belajar jadi orang benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:11.71,0:17:15.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mulai dari cuci piring,\Nupah 650 yen per jam.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.17,0:17:17.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makan kami sediakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dapat tenaga kerja, deh.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:19.10,0:17:20.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita sama-sama berusaha, ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.63,0:17:22.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,650 yen per jam?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Murah banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:26.08,0:17:27.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koichi, sudah hampir waktunya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.85,0:17:29.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari ini kau ada wawancara siang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:29.96,0:17:31.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oh iya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.20,0:17:33.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya sudah, kami pergi dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.43,0:17:34.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Ah, anu...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:34.82,0:17:35.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bolehkah kita...
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.90,0:17:37.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Foto bareng?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:38.40,0:17:40.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke, aku foto, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:40.03,0:17:41.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.99,0:17:44.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo cepat! Nanti terlambat!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.26,0:17:46.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Boleh Pop bergabung dengan kami juga?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.66,0:18:06.23,dialog - atas,,0,0,0,,Sejujurnya, perusahaan kami ini\Nkurang diminati lulusan universitas.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.39,0:18:10.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kerjanya di lapangan kebersihan.\NBerat dan kotor...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:10.48,0:18:12.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak masalah?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:12.63,0:18:13.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bos...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.78,0:18:16.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ah, saya tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.30,0:18:19.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saya malah sering membersihkan\Nsampah dan selokan sebagai hobi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:19.63,0:18:22.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hobi? Kau aneh juga, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:22.40,0:18:24.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bos, tolong...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.00,0:18:26.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baik, pertanyaan berikutnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.75,0:18:31.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haimawari Koichi, bekal seumur hidup apa
Dialogue: 10,0:18:31.25,0:18:34.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang kau dapatkan di masa sekolah?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.48,0:18:35.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.89,0:18:43.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pengalaman dari kegiatan relawan\Ndi lingkungan sekitar,
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.76,0:18:45.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan teman-temanku!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.66,0:18:50.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menurutku wawancara hari ini\Nberjalan lumayan baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:50.86,0:18:52.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semoga lancar.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.81,0:18:56.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Perusahaannya kecil, tapi\Ndirekturnya kelihatan seperti orang baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.40,0:19:00.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jujur saja, selama ada yang mau menerima,\Ndi mana pun tak masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:00.20,0:19:03.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memangnya tak apa memutuskan kerja\Nseperti itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.03,0:19:05.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak punya mimpi di masa depan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:05.66,0:19:08.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hm, mimpi, ya...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau mimpi, rasanya sudah tercapai.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.25,0:19:15.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih dari tiga tahun di kota ini,\Naku jadi pahlawan gadungan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:15.50,0:19:20.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tiap hari terasa seru,\Ndan banyak orang yang berterima kasih.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.55,0:19:23.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dan untungnya,\Naku tak pernah ditangkap polisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.50,0:19:26.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagian itu cukup berbahaya, sih.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:26.52,0:19:30.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bisa dibilang hampir semua hal yang ingin\Nkulakukan waktu kecil sudah tercapai.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.50,0:19:35.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kini aku tinggal cari kerja yang benar\Ndan bisa menghidupi diri sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:35.50,0:19:37.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Agar orang tuaku juga tenang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.10,0:19:40.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau terdengar seperti orang\Nyang bertanggung jawab.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:40.95,0:19:43.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke, perbaikan selesai!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:43.66,0:19:47.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi yang ini juga sudah mulai usang.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:50.86,0:19:53.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saatnya pakai yang baru.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.20,0:19:55.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yang terakhir.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:56.36,0:20:00.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Koleksi hoodie-mu habis dipakai\Nsemua dalam tiga tahun, ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:00.80,0:20:02.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Padahal kau sangat menyayanginya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.36,0:20:05.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekarang juga masih sayang!\NTakkan kubuang!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:05.36,0:20:07.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Takkan kuambil juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.56,0:20:12.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Yah, kalau sudah dapat kerja, aku tak bisa\Nmain jadi pahlawan lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau yang ini rusak juga,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.16,0:20:18.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,mungkin saatnya The Crawler lulus.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.10,0:20:21.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lulus?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:22.60,0:20:24.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku terlihat keren.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.62,0:20:28.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lulus...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.63,0:20:30.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pop.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,A-Apa? Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:33.09,0:20:35.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau patroli sekarang?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:35.54,0:20:37.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau mencoba hoodie baru!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.96,0:20:40.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, tunggu, aku siap-siap dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.86,0:20:43.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oke! Ayo berangkat!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:43.56,0:20:45.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu dulu, dong!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.10,0:20:54.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Musim panas tahun keempat kuliah.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.81,0:20:57.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Musim terakhir The Crawler.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.90,0:21:01.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai musim ini berakhir...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.61,0:21:05.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pahlawan gadungan?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.40,0:21:08.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Vigilante? Yah, terserah...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.04,0:21:12.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan terus meluncur sampai akhir!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:55.90,0:22:57.48,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dokter.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.48,0:23:00.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kondisi sampel?
Dialogue: 10,0:23:02.40,0:23:04.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak ada masalah dengan penyesuaiannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.65,0:23:10.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebentar lagi mencapai level praktis\Ntanpa perlu perawatan.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.16,0:23:14.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, mari kita lanjutkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.10,0:23:21.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Eksperimen besar kita, milikku dan dia.
